commit.message:
op-common.h (_FP_MUL, [...]): Add /* FALLTHRU */ comments.

	* soft-fp/op-common.h (_FP_MUL, _FP_FMA, _FP_DIV): Add
	/* FALLTHRU */ comments.

From-SVN: r244884

+	/* FALLTHRU */ comments.
+
 2017-01-21  Gerald Pfeifer  <gerald@pfeifer.com>
 
 	* config/i386/cygming-crtbegin.c (LIBGCJ_SONAME): No longer #define.
